Introduction¶

This is a dataset for Ford GoBike Service for Feb - 2019 , It consists of 170 K information about the trip and the users such as thier gender and age.

Ford GoBike is the Bay Areas bike share system. Bay Area Bike Share was introduced in 2013. It services San Francisco, the East Bay and San Jose. Similar to other bike share systems, Ford GoBike consists of a fleet of bikes that can be unlocked in one station and returned in any other network station. Thus, this is ideal for one-way trips. These bikes are available for use thorughout the year and riders have access to all bikes in the network.

Dataset Dictionary:

1- duration_sec: Trip Duration

2- start_time :start time for each trip

3- end_time : end time for each trip

4- start_station_id

5- start_station_name

6- start_station_latitude

7- start_station_longitude

8- end_station_id

9- end_station_name

10- end_station_latitude

11- end_station_longitude

12- bike_id

13- user_type: User Type (Subscriber or Customer Subscriber = Member or Customer = Casual)

14 - member_birth_year: Member Year of Birth

15member_gender

16- bike_share_for_all_trip: Boolean to track members who are enrolled in the "Bike Share for All" program for low-income residents

Gender of Ford GoBike Users¶

Males use the Ford GoBike service more than females, where 74.4% of males and 23.5% females using the service.

Weekdays of Ford GoBike rides¶

1- In the weekdays people use the Ford GoBike service more than the weekends.

2- Thursday has the highest trips.

3- Saturday and Sunday which are the weekend days has the less use of the service.

Subscribers VS Customers¶

1- As shown in the figure users who are subscribe are more than customer users.

2 - The subscriber riders achive 90.4% rides , and 9.6% from the trips are customers.

Top 20 startoff stations¶

Bike Share for All Program¶

The number of memebers who did not enrolled in the program are more than who did , which 90.3% didn't enrolled and just 9.7% enrolled.

Duration of Trips¶

1- The number of trips refernce to the duration in min is skewed to the right.

2- The average duration of the total trips in min is 11.7 min .

3- The minimum duration of the trips is 1.0 min and the max is 1409 min.
